BrainKiller DemoRelease 1.0

Code: Virtual Madness
Publisher: TitanComputer


Brain Killer is a new shoot `em up 3D action game for all Amigas
with CPU 68020
     4 MB Fast RAM
     minimum Graffiticard better AGA

This is AGA only demo, at the moment. Graffiti support coming soon.

Demo needs around 4Mb of harddisc space.

~        =    Map
LSHIFT   =    launch mine
LAlt     =    kick
LAmiga   =    fire current weapon
RShift   =    hand grenades
return   =    open door
1        =    fists
6        =    machine gun
8        =    rocket launcher


watch out our website: http://www.vossnet.de/titanhb/       for further
details.
Release July/August `97


Suggestions for new game features are welcome. E-Mail us: TitanHB@vossnet.de


